Amatsu-Mikaboshi, the August Star of Heaven, is the Japanese god of evil, the kami who oversees all that goes on under cover of darkness. He sees the hearts of all men and women, and the owners of the vilest hearts he claims. 
Amatsu-Mikaboshi is a lawful evil intermediate deity. His Realm, The Brilliant Land, is in Avalas, the first Layer of Acheron. He manifests as an old man made of shadow, or as an alluring woman. 
Source
Legends &amp; Lore (D&amp;D 2.0)